# Handwritten Text Translator 🔤🎧

This web application extracts text from **printed or handwritten (cursive supported) English images**, translates it into multiple languages, and generates **audio output** in the selected language.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Supports **handwritten & printed text**
- Cursive handwriting supported
- OCR using EasyOCR
- Translation to:
  - English
  - Hindi
  - Kannada
  - Telugu
  - Tamil
- Text-to-Speech output
- Audio is **not stored permanently**

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python
- Flask
- EasyOCR
- OpenCV
- Google Translate
- gTTS
- HTML/CSS

---

## ▶️ How to Run

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/handwritten-text-translator.git
cd handwritten-text-translator
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py